paragraphs.title: Normal Scala/Java Set
paragraphs.text:
import com.madhukaraphatak.sizeof.SizeEstimator

val memorySizeString = SizeEstimator.estimate("abc");

val set = (Set(1) ++ Set(2,3) ++ Set(3,4) ++ Set(5))
val memorySizeSet = SizeEstimator.estimate(set)

paragraphs.title: Bloom Filter
paragraphs.text:
import com.twitter.algebird.BloomFilterAggregator

val bfAgg = BloomFilterAggregator(5, 64, 0)

val set = (Set(1) ++ Set(2,3) ++ Set(3,4) ++ Set(5))
val memorySizeSet = SizeEstimator.estimate(set)

val bfAggs = bfAgg(List("1")) ++ bfAgg(List("2","3")) ++ bfAgg(List("3","4")) ++ bfAgg(List("5"))
val memorySizeSet = SizeEstimator.estimate(bfAggs)

bfAggs.contains("3")
